## ğŸš€ Features

- ğŸ” Offline wallet generation using post-quantum cryptography

- ğŸ§¬ Dilithium5 digital signatures for quantum-safe authentication

- ğŸ”’ SHA3-512 hashing for data integrity

- ğŸŒ Mesh VPN integration with WireGuard

- ğŸ§  Compatible with [PQClean](https://github.com/pqclean/pqclean), [Pyshark](https://github.com/KimiNewt/pyshark), [Scapy](https://github.com/secdev/scapy), and Logging4

- ğŸ¦Š Designed for [Bit512](https://github.com/kitohamachi/bit512) â€” the currency of the next millennium

